body.name: Fixwal Shoe Rack with Covers, 9 Tier Tall Shoe Rack with 2 Large Pockets Dustproof Narrow Shoe Rack Organizer for Closet Entryway Holds 18-20 Pairs Black Metal Shoe Shelf Stand
features: Dustproof Cover & Non-woven Layers - The shoe rack for closet coming with a premium dustproof cover can protect your shoes from dust. Moreover, the cover of tall shoe rack is designed with two side pockets where you can additionally store your keys, gloves and other gadgets. And the non-woven layers can effectively keep dust off the lower shoes, which is also easier to put high heels

Detachable & Freely DIY Install - The shoe rack organizer can be dividable and assembled as 9 tier shoe rack, or as 5 tier plus 4 tier shoe shelf stand or any tier you wish. The height of each single layer is about 6.7” but you can remove 1-2 layers off to make larger space for your long boots or storage boxes

Large Capacity & Space Saving - Our metal shoe rack with 2 side pockets offers more storage space, 17.7"L x 11.8"W x 60.3"H, can accommodate 18-20 pairs of shoes with easy. Most importantly, Fixwal 9 tier narrow shoe rack can fit in small space while providing much room to keep your shoes clean and organized

Sturdy & Easy to Assemble - Our free standing shoe rack organizer cabinet is made of upgraded 13mm corrosion-resistant metal pipes and strengthened PP connectors, which provides better stability and load capacity. Installation is as easy as ABC

Anywhere - Our shoe rack for entryway can be placed anywhere like front door, entryway, garage, which is not only for shoes, but also for books, toys, boxes. You can freely disassembled and DIY as you want to store different types of shoes

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Fixwal is committed to creating simple and organized home life with higher quality and more reasonable prices. We hope to create better living experience for your limited space. Our products provide solutions for organizing and decorating your daily space, helping you to stay away from clutter. Simple life starts from home! Fixwal 9 Tiers Shoe Rack Organizer Taller & narrow shoe storage cabinet, perfect size for small space, can storage 18-20 pairs of shoesYou can remove one layer to fit boots or other different needsThis multifunctional shoe organizer can storage shoes, boots, clothes, bags, for closets, enteyway, garage and bedroomThis 9-Tier shoe rack shelf will keep your house well-organized

Waterproof Non-woven Cover and Layers The dustproof cover and shoe rack layer are made of waterproof non-woven, and cleaning is super easy. Just wipe it with a wet cloth if needed. Sturdy and Durable Design The metal tubes and PP connectors enable our shoe rack maintain a sturdy structure and won't fall apart. Powder-coated Metal Tubes The powder-coated metal tube prevents the surface of the shoe rack from rusting or corroding, making the shoe self more durable.

Door with Velcro There is a Velcro in the front of the dust cover. You can roll up the curtain for easy access or storage of shoes. Door with zipper The dust cover is designed with a zipper so that you can zip it up to keep dust off your shoes, providing you a more tidy home. 2 Side Pockets Pockets on the sides of the dust cover add extra storage space and can be used to store light items such as keys, socks and slippers.

Q1: Is assembly difficult? A1. Easy to install, with installation instructions, small wooden hammer and gloves for quick installation. Q2: Is it stable to use? A2: Yes, this shoe rack organizer is made of the 13mm metal frames and durable non-woven fabric layers, can fit 18-20 pairs of shoes. Q3: How many shoes can be placed on one layer of the shoe rack? A:3 Up to 2-3 pairs of shoes. The size of this shoe rack is 17.7"W * 11.8"D * 60.3"H, and the layer distance is 6.7''. Q4: Can this shoe rack be disassembled? A4: Yes, any layer of the shoe rack can be disassembled, so that one shoe rack becomes two shoe racks, or the layer spacing can be adjusted to meet the needs of placing boots. Q5: What is the tallest shoe or item that can be placed on the shelf? A5: The shoe organizer has 9 layers, the height of the middle can be adjusted by increasing or reducing the number of layers, it can be adjusted according to your needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars nice rack that takes up little space!
reviews.reviewText: This shoe rack is very light so can fall over easy if you don't have enough weight on it. it does make our entry way look a lot nicer though as we just had our shoes in a storage tote that we would just throw our shoes into. It was pretty simple to put together maybe took about 15 or 20 minutes to finish it up. Light and simple packaging. the rack is great for tight fit small spaces! The cover is nice as well so you dont have to just have all your shoes on display when guests are over, or you can probably use the rack as just storage for shoes that are not in use to put away in the closet!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I got this because I have a very small closet with no place to put my shoes. This was easy to put together and I have it stored right behind the door so it’s not really in my line of sight in my room. I love that it can zip closed to help keep dust out. I’m incredibly happy with it.
